title: Friends and Neighbors Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Take-out, Vietnamese, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy little eatery with a small town diner feel. Offers a Vietnamese food menu as well as a western menu with sandwiches, burgers, fries, etc. The separate vegetarian menu section features veggie sandwiches, burgers, and Asian dishes.
